	<body class="- topic/body " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/git-tech-writers/common_workflows.dita" xtrc="body:1;8:8">
		<p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/git-tech-writers/common_workflows.dita" xtrc="p:1;9:6">Workflows are <xref href="https://www.atlassian.com/git/tutorials/comparing-workflows" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/git-tech-writers/common_workflows.dita" xtrc="xref:1;10:35"><?ditaot usertext?>recipes</xref> for working and collaborating
			successfully on a Git project.</p>
		<p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/git-tech-writers/common_workflows.dita" xtrc="p:2;12:6">Common workflows for working with Git:<ul id="ul_trs_fn3_wwb" class="- topic/ul " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/git-tech-writers/common_workflows.dita" xtrc="ul:1;12:68">
				<li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/git-tech-writers/common_workflows.dita" xtrc="li:1;13:9"><xref href="centralized_workflow.dita" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/git-tech-writers/common_workflows.dita" xtrc="xref:2;13:49" type="topic"><?ditaot gentext?>Centralized Workflow</xref></li>
